@startuml
title How the areas connect: two end-to-end chains
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam activity {
  BackgroundColor #E9EDF5
  BorderColor #26386B
  DiamondBackgroundColor #E9EDF5
  DiamondBorderColor #26386B
}
skinparam ArrowColor #26386B

|Payment chain|
start
:pain — customer initiates a payment;
:pacs — banks clear and settle it;
:camt — balances and entries reported;
stop

|Securities chain|
start
:secl — CCP clears the trade;
:colr — collateral covers the exposure;
:sese — securities and cash settle;
:semt — holdings and transactions reported;
:auth — the activity is reported to regulators;
stop
@enduml
